overview.en: The SEGG blockchain utilizes the ERC20 Ethereum underlying protocol and can be trusted as a payment gateway. The platform is driven by the community, and the logic is determined by pre-released smart contracts that no central organization can manipulate. It has extremely high stability and extremely low collision degree, completely eliminating the possibility of brute force.
overview.zh: SEGG 区块链利用ERC20以太坊底层协议，可信任第三方作为支付网关。平台由社区驱动开发，逻辑由事先发布的智能合约决定，没有中心组织可以操纵。具有极高的稳定性和极低的碰撞程度，完全排除暴力破解可能。
